# 1. Ignore everything in the project by default
*

# 2. Keep essential RStudio settings
!.gitignore
!*.Rproj

# 3. Allow Git to look inside the Code folder
!Code/

# 4. Explicitly ignore everything INSIDE Code by default
Code/*

# 5. Make the absolute exception for your ONE file
!Code/NationalRegressions_System_Peer_Pressure_Commented.R

